Class VariableGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.VariableGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<VariableGroup>

    @Entity
public final class VariableGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<VariableGroup>

    Represents a group of Variables, usually for display grouping.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
